# packages/twenty-server/src/front/ is INTENTIONALLY tracked on deploy branches:
# pre-built twenty-front bundle so Deno Deploy's 5-min build cap doesn't have
# to re-run vite for twenty-front + workspace deps; the install command still
# builds twenty-shared/emails/client-sdk dists fresh.
